comment on column {{CallCentre_PRE_BUS_V}}.model_prediction.model_key is 'Model identifier, e.g. call_quality_v1, coaching_priority_v2. Separates predictions from different models.';
comment on column {{CallCentre_PRE_BUS_V}}.model_prediction.entity_type is 'Entity type discriminator. Default CALL. Allows table to store features for other entity types in future.';

comment on column {{CallCentre_PRE_BUS_V}}.model_prediction.prediction_json is 'Flexible JSON payload for complex prediction outputs supplementing scalar prediction_value and prediction_class.';
